reviewText: Be prepared for the most life changing preaching ! I was so touched I had to buy it to give it to someone else

Good message. He hit on certain topics that pertained to my life. I bought product in order to share with others and listen to again bc what I saw on television is the same thing I heard on cd. Good job T.D. Jakes!
I received the product in good time and good condition. Very good CD by Bishop TD Jakes. An eye opener and encouraging as well as life changing.

My teacher chose this CD for a class paper. It was used to help the class to break the issues in their life, so we could see Gods purpose for our life, a lot of people were bless by this CD, to God be the Glory!

I was very disappointed to find out this item was not a DVD but a CD instead. I already have this item as a CD from the same package. The message is awesome and all but I was looking for a visual to the audio. Please change the description of this item so others don not get mislead like I was.
